  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 200°C (400°F) for 10 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together coconut oil, mildly hot sauce, nutty ghee, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add chopped onion and bell pepper to the bowl and toss to coat.",
    "Cut chicken breast into 1-inch pieces and add to the bowl, tossing to coat.",
    "Thread chicken, onion, and bell pepper onto skewers.",
    "Brush coconut oil on both sides of skewers.",
    "Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until chicken is cooked through.",
    "Let skewers rest for 2 minutes before serving."
